metadata.name: PAPERS.I #11
metadata.description:
The PAPERS series is an attempt to reflect my graphic design background and printing experience which are an essential part of my professional identity. I think printing and especially hand printing is quite similar to modern generative art. All prints are made with the same clichÃ© or idea but slightly differ from each other.
This piece was inspired by the works of Karel Martens (b.1939) â€” a Dutch graphic designer and artist. His experiments with stamping by ready-made objects were very important for my understanding of how printing generally works.

Made with p5js.
Press the space button to save a high-res JPG.
